Package: stdictkr
Title: Data Package using Korean Standard Dictionary
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Chanyub",
             family = "Park",
             role = c("aut","cre"),
             email = "mrchypark@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6474-2570"))
Description: stdictkr is a client package that uses the API provided by 
        'the Korean standard dictionary' <https://stdict.korean.go.kr/openapi/openApiInfo.do>.
        You can also directly download a dictionary and use it as a tibble data type.
